REGAIN Design System & Aesthetic Rules
Core Design Philosophy
Slick, Seamless, Minimalist Black & White Aesthetic
Pure black background with white text and glassmorphism elements
Smooth, fluid transitions and animations throughout
Clean, modern interface with subtle depth through glass effects
Apple-inspired interactions with precise timing and easing
Color Palette
Primary Colors
Background: #000000 (Pure black)
Primary Text: #FFFFFF (Pure white)
Text on White Elements: #000000 (Black - for text on white backgrounds/sliders)
Glassmorphism Colors
Standard Glass Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)
Strong Glass Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)
Glass Border (Standard): rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)
Glass Border (Strong): rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15)
Glass Border (Hover): rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) to rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)
Text Opacity Variations
Primary Text: #FFFFFF (100% opacity)
Secondary Text: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7) (70% opacity)
Tertiary Text: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6) (60% opacity)
Muted Text: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) (50% opacity)
Disabled/Other Month: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) (30% opacity)
Special Cases
Active Navigation Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)
Hover Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)
Dark Overlay Background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) to rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)
White Slider Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95)
Typography
Font Family
Primary Font: 'Inter', sans-serif (applied globally)
Font Weights Available: 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800
Font Size Hierarchy
Large Headings: 2xl-5xl (24px-48px), font-weight: 700-800
Medium Headings: xl-2xl (20px-24px), font-weight: 600-700
Small Headings: lg (18px), font-weight: 600
Body Text: base (16px), font-weight: 400-500
Small Text: sm (14px), font-weight: 400-500
Extra Small Text: xs (12px-13px), font-weight: 400-500
Tiny Text: 11px, font-weight: 400-500
Text Styling Rules
All text must be white (#FFFFFF) on black backgrounds
Text on white elements (sliders, active states) must be black (#000000)
Use opacity variations for hierarchy, not color changes
Maintain consistent font-weight for similar element types
Glassmorphism Effects
Standard Glass (.glass)
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);backdrop-filter: blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
Strong Glass (.glass-strong)
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);backdrop-filter: blur(30px);-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(30px);border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
Glassmorphism Rules
Always include both backdrop-filter and -webkit-backdrop-filter for browser compatibility
Border opacity: 0.1 (standard) to 0.15 (strong)
Background opacity: 0.05 (standard) to 0.08 (strong)
Blur amount: 20px (standard) to 30px (strong)
Border Radius
Small Elements (buttons, inputs, small cards): 0.5rem (8px) to 0.75rem (12px)
Medium Elements (cards, containers): 1rem (16px) to 1.5rem (24px)
Large Elements (major containers, modals): 1.5rem (24px) to 2rem (32px)
Pill-shaped Elements (toggles, badges): 50% or 9999px
Circular Elements: 50%
Transitions & Animations
Standard Transition
For all interactive elements (buttons, links, cards, etc.):
transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
Page Transitions
Fade-in animation for page content:
animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out;@keyframes fadeIn {    from {        opacity: 0;        transform: translateY(10px);    }    to {        opacity: 1;        transform: translateY(0);    }}
Progress Bar Animation
For progress bars and width-based animations:
transition: width 1s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
Pulse Animation
For attention-grabbing elements (FAB, notifications):
@keyframes pulse {    0%, 100% {        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);    }    50% {        box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);    }}animation: pulse 2s infinite;
Transition Timing Rules
Fast Interactions: 0.2s - 0.3s (buttons, hovers)
Medium Transitions: 0.3s - 0.4s (page changes, card states)
Slow Animations: 0.4s - 1s (progress bars, complex animations)
Easing Function: Always use cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) for smooth, natural motion
Hover Effects
Card Hover (.card-hover)
.card-hover:hover {    transform: translateY(-2px);    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);}
Navigation Item Hover
.nav-item:hover {    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);    transform: translateX(4px);}
Button Hover
button:hover {    transform: scale(1.02) to scale(1.1);    /* Background opacity increase */    /* Border color brightening */}
Button Active State
button:active {    transform: scale(0.95) to scale(0.98);}
Hover Effect Rules
Always use subtle transforms (translateY, translateX, scale)
Increase border opacity on hover (0.1 → 0.2 → 0.3)
Slightly increase background opacity on hover
Maintain smooth transitions (0.3s cubic-bezier)
Shadows & Depth
Box Shadows
Subtle Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) (for sliders, elevated elements)
Medium Shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) (for cards on hover)
White Glow Shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) (for pulse effects)
Depth Hierarchy
Use glassmorphism opacity for depth (lower opacity = more depth)
Border opacity indicates elevation (higher opacity = more elevated)
Subtle shadows for major interactive elements only
