Design Principles
Seamless & Fluid: All interactions should feel smooth and connected
Minimal Contrast: Use opacity variations, not color changes
Subtle Depth: Glassmorphism creates layering without heavy shadows
Precision Timing: All animations use consistent easing and durations
Black & White Only: No colors except black, white, and their opacity variations
Consistent Glassmorphism: All elevated elements use glass effects
Smooth Transitions: Every interactive element has hover/active states
Clean Typography: Inter font family, clear hierarchy through weight and size
Pulse for Attention: Use pulse animation sparingly for important elements
Apple-inspired Interactions: Precise, polished, and refined feel
