[ ] Has hover effect with transform (translateY, translateX, or scale)
[ ] Uses standard transition timing (0.3s cubic-bezier)
[ ] Text is white on black, black on white elements
[ ] Border opacity follows hierarchy (0.1 → 0.15 → 0.2 → 0.3)
[ ] Border radius is consistent with element size
[ ] Includes both backdrop-filter and -webkit-backdrop-filter
[ ] Active states have appropriate visual feedback
[ ] Follows spacing and padding guidelines
[ ] Maintains the slick, seamless aesthetic